wikipedia_page.main: James "Jazza" Dickens (born 12 April 1991) is a British professional boxer who challenged for the WBA (Super) super bantamweight title in 2016 and the IBF featherweight title in 2021. At national level, he held the British super bantamweight title from 2015 to 2017.
